OL,4,Cheating at some point this winter
OL,6,FMore than one in five Welsh have gone
OL,7,Fwithout heating their home at some
OL,8,Fpoint this winter, while 13% have gone
OL,9,Fwithout a shower or a bath.
OL,11,FA survey by the Bevan Foundation,
OL,12,Fshared exclusively with , also found
OL,13,Fone in ten pensioners have cut down,
OL,14,For skipped meals altogether, while 8%
OL,15,Fhave decided against taking an
OL,16,Fessential journey like attending a
OL,17,Fmedical appointment.
