OL,6,FPercentages though, tell only part of
OL,7,Fthe story, as the average age of the
OL,8,FUK population continues to climb. The
OL,9,Fnumber of people over the age of 85 in
OL,10,Fthe UK is expected to double by 2050.
OL,12,FNowhere is this felt more keenly than
OL,13,Fin Wales, where 21.4% of the
OL,14,Fpopulation are over 65, compared to
OL,15,F18.7% across the UK.
OL,17,FITV News has travelled around the
OL,18,Fcountry hearing from pensioners unable
OL,19,Fto make ends meet from their state
OL,20,Fpensions, as well as the struggling to
OL,21,Fhelp them.
