OL,6,FAlan, 77, lives in Duffryn, on the
OL,7,Foutskirts of . He was a communications
OL,8,Fofficer in the Royal Navy, travelling
OL,9,Fto every continent in nearly twenty
OL,10,Fyears of service.
OL,12,FHe was forced to leave the armed
OL,13,Fforces on medical grounds two years
OL,14,Fbefore he became entitled to a
OL,15,Fmilitary pension. After he pays all
OL,16,Fhis bills, he has next to nothing left.
OL,18,F"You've got to be very careful about
OL,19,Fhow you spend, and what you spend your
OL,20,Fmoney on," he tells me.
