OL,6,FEach day Alan eats the same meal and
OL,7,Fwears his winter coat in his small
OL,8,Fflat so that he can avoid putting the
OL,9,Fheating on for longer than two hours a
OL,10,Fday. He says he would love to enjoy
OL,11,Fhis retirement and make friends, but
OL,12,Fit's too expensive.
OL,14,FHe said: "There is no such thing, for
OL,15,Fme, as a social life...I'd love a
OL,16,Fsocial life, but I can't afford it,
OL,17,Fliterally."
