OL,6,FHe said: "Those cost of living
OL,7,Fpayments eased a lot of the pressure
OL,8,Fthat people faced, and they're not
OL,9,Fthere this year, even though the
OL,10,Ffinancial pressures are very much the
OL,11,Fsame.
OL,13,F"Without that extra support, people
OL,14,Fare finding life much more difficult.
OL,15,FWe need to be giving that money and
OL,16,Fputting it back into people's pockets
OL,17,Fbecause that will ultimately reduce
OL,18,Fpressure on our and other public
OL,19,Fservices as well."
